        <abstract>
            <p>CD thinks HBD’s tables would be a considerable gain because "the importance of hereditary transmission can hardly be exaggerated from every point of view". Makes suggestions.</p>
            <p>Asks him to send any remarkable cases of inheritance to him and, as well, any case of regrowth of amputated additional digit.</p>
        </abstract>
